<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="D" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Daw" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Daw,</orth> the bird Corvus monedula, jackdaw: <bibl n="shak. ado 2.3.264" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado II, 3, 264</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lll 5.2.915" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL V, 2, 915</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tn 3.4.39" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. III, 4, 39</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tro 1.2.265" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. I, 2, 265</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. oth 1.1.65" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. I, 1, 65</bibl>. Thought a foolish bird: <cit><quote>I am no wiser than a d.</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h6 2.4.18" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A II, 4, 18</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>then thou dwellest with --s too? No, I serve not thy master,</quote> <bibl n="shak. cor 4.5.48" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. IV, 5, 48</bibl></cit>.
